name: Wifi-car
tagline: Easily build a Wi-Fi car with open source technologies
body:
### Welcome to WiFi Car project
The WiFi Car uses variety of open source technologies, such as OpenWrt, Arduino etc. Get started:

```
$ git clone https://github.com/xiongyihui/wifi-car.git
```

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with WiFi Car? Check out the documentation at https://github.com/xiongyihui/wifi-car/wiki or contact xiongyihui3@gmail.com.
